38#ifndef __COMPILE_ET_H__
39#define __COMPILE_ET_H__
40
41#include <config.h>
42
43#include <err.h>
44#include <stdio.h>
45#include <string.h>
46#include <stdlib.h>
47#include <stdarg.h>
48#include <ctype.h>
49#include <roken.h>
50
51extern long base_id;
52extern int number;
53extern char *prefix;
54extern char name[128];
55extern char *id_str;
56extern char *filename;
57extern int numerror;
58
59struct error_code {
60 unsigned number;
61 char *name;
62 char *string;
63 struct error_code *next, **tail;
64};
65
66extern struct error_code *codes;
67
68#define APPEND(L, V) \
69do { \
70 if((L) == NULL) { \
71 (L) = (V); \
72 (L)->tail = &(V)->next; \
73 (L)->next = NULL; \
74 }else{ \
75 *(L)->tail = (V); \
76 (L)->tail = &(V)->next; \
77 } \
78}while(0)
79
80#endif /* __COMPILE_ET_H__ */
